articles.author: Rafiq Maqbool and Ashok Sharma, The Associated Press
articles.title: India launches submarine, warships to counter China in Indian Ocean - Defense News
articles.description: The move underscores the importance of protecting the Indian Ocean region through which 95% of the country’s trade moves amid a strong Chinese presence.
